# Joke & Meme Generator

## Description
This is a fun web application that generates random jokes and popular memes. Users can click on buttons to fetch new jokes and memes, making it an entertaining way to pass the time.

## Features
- Fetches random jokes from a third-party API and displays them on the page.
- Retrieves popular memes from another third-party API and showcases them to users.
- Users can click on buttons to get new jokes and memes, providing an interactive experience.
- Fun and visually appealing design with styled buttons and content containers.

## Third-Party APIs Used
1. **Official Joke API**: This API provides random jokes with setup and punchline. [API Link](https://official-joke-api.appspot.com/random_joke)
2. **Imgflip API**: This API fetches popular memes for display. [API Link](https://api.imgflip.com/get_memes)

## How to Use
1. Open the web application in a browser.
2. Click on the "Get Another Joke" button to fetch a new joke.
3. Click on the "Get Another Meme" button to fetch a new meme.
4. Enjoy the jokes and memes!

## Installation
No installation required. Simply open the `index.html` file in a web browser to run the application.

